title: The League Season 5 (720p)
description:
Complete fifth season of The League, in HD. I noticed that no one has uploaded a torrent for season five, HD or not, so I decided to gather the files myself.

I fixed something when making the torrent, for episodes nine and ten, when they were uploaded, episode nine was labeled as ten so when they uploaded episode ten, they put REAL in the file name, since this is a complete season, I changed episode nine from ten to nine and took the REAL out of the episode ten file name.

Info from episode one (used MediaInfo this time):

Video:
1280x720 (16:9) 23.976 fps H264/AVC (5,404 kbps)

Audio:
English 2.0 Stereo AC3 (384 kbps)

I will be seeding forever, but I can't 24/7 so the initial seeding will be a problem, since the size is over 10 gigs, so if you seed after downloading, thank you, and thank you to the people who uploaded the episodes!
